0. cuda, cudnn 설치 확인
$ cat /usr/local/cuda/include/cudnn.h | grep CUDNN_MAJOR -A 2
$ nvcc --version

1. ~/.bashrc 편집 
$ sudo vi ~/.bashrc

맨 밑에 다음 내용 추가 
$ export PATH=/usr/local/cuda-9.0/bin${PATH:+:${PATH}}
$ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/cuda/lib64:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:+:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH}}

2. ~/.bashrc 변경사항 적용 
$ source ~/.bashrc
